        <mxCell id="OaPi2JGeNaKhquKWLYuI-5" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;" value="&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Http&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;- flexible in define data in json&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- text-based&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;-it serialize both field name and value -&amp;gt; adding data&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- when transferring binary file by json, http need to convert it to text (&lt;b&gt;byte -&amp;gt; base64&lt;/b&gt; ) -&amp;gt; &lt;u&gt;adding 33% to len of data&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;+each 3 bytes we convert to 4 block, each block 6-bits, each 6&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;bits&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot; data-end=&quot;177&quot; data-start=&quot;163&quot;&gt;equivalent with a charater in Base-64&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot; data-end=&quot;177&quot; data-start=&quot;163&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;+ so cost 4 charater(~4 bytes) for 3 bytes data( increase 33%)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="140" width="330" x="1200" y="1040" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="OaPi2JGeNaKhquKWLYuI-6" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;" value="&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;RPC&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;- based on contract, each side need to apply contract when calling api&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- binary protocol&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- just serialize value bf of knowing structure of both side&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="120" width="350" x="1530" y="1040" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
