        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="xFSQszVZrvHgohZOU4dA-18" value="&lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Topics of reliability&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;Property need to safe from partial failure&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1010" y="377.5" width="170" height="65" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="YSBGgVX1vi0a6HuOUv6A-1" value="&lt;b&gt;Reliability&lt;/b&gt; :&amp;nbsp;&lt;div&gt;- system continue to function correctly if presence of partial of failure&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Measured as the probability of a system working correctly &lt;b&gt;in a given time&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;u&gt;- rarely failure happen&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(153, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;R(t) = e^(t/MTBF)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt; -- &lt;b&gt;t&lt;/b&gt; : time of mission need system work correctly&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; -- &lt;b&gt;MTBF&lt;/b&gt; : average time between two failure event&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;ex : finance, data safety&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1260" y="460" width="430" height="90" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="YSBGgVX1vi0a6HuOUv6A-2" value="&lt;b&gt;Availability&lt;/b&gt; :&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- probability of system work correctly in &lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;any given time ( including fix time)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- expecting to &lt;b&gt;recover quickly&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;u&gt;- failures can happen frequently but recover quickly -&amp;gt; user ignore&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(153, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Availability(A) = MTBF/(MTBF + MTTR)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt; -- &lt;b&gt;MTTR&lt;/b&gt; : mean( average) time to repair&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;ex : streaming, social media&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;" vertex="1" parent="1">
