        <mxCell id="YSBGgVX1vi0a6HuOUv6A-44" value="&lt;div&gt;Active redundancy - Hot spare&lt;/div&gt;- all node do processing&lt;div&gt;- ideal for provide high availability&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- handle&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;state consistency&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;" vertex="1" parent="1">
