        <mxCell id="HIalZ3uUfE1h6-yRsq41-3" value="&lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Content server&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;div&gt;- write operation no have change to be config because of data is immutable&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;" vertex="1" parent="1">
