        <mxCell id="ofon12ZNKnvjW4MxqfXj-21" value="&lt;b&gt;Virtual IP&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;- primary and standby have it own ip address&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- additionally, we have a Floating IP -&amp;gt; can be assign to any instance&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- when a issue happen in an instance -&amp;gt; the others init protocol to&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;transfer IP point to primary -&amp;gt; to standby&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;" vertex="1" parent="1">
