        <mxCell id="8wiF6pRVqLy2-9FtFak7-19" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(204, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;u style=&quot;&quot;&gt;SSL&amp;nbsp;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;* server transfer public key in certification&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;*&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;client generate + transfer symmetric key&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;* both client and server use symmetric key to encryption and decryption&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;* using symmetric key because it is more fast and efficient&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
