        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="8Y3Pc1Z9YDT49znb_Rtu-4" value="3 Steps&lt;div&gt;+ 3 steps is enough to ensure that both sides have received the packet&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;+ both side need send it&#39;s&amp;nbsp;ISNc and acknowledge when the orther peer has receive packet&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;=&amp;gt; to optimize , 2 step are combined, so 3 steps is enough, 2 is lack of steps and 4 is&amp;nbsp;redundant&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;fontSize=10;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;dashed=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
